items.title: Sebi probes six local investment banks over handling of small IPOs
items.description: The investigations follow efforts by Sebi to warn investors about the dangers of investing in some small businesses as well as plans for tighter rules for such IPOS

items.title: NTPC Green Energy urges Sebi to expedite approval for Rs 10K crore IPO
items.description: State-owned power generator also seeking leeway on certain listing regulations

items.title: Swiggy gets Sebi go-ahead for IPO launch, set for stock market debut
items.description: Before Swiggy launches its IPO, it will have to place its updated draft red herring prospectus (UDRHP) in the public domain for at least 21 days
